<h1 style="margin-top:20px">A 1990s thriller fiction book by Dean Koontz actually features a &#39;Wuhan-400&#39; virus outbreak</h1>
<p class="subtitle">If you make enough predictions, one is bound to come true.</p>
<div class="publish-info">
<p>
<span class="non-date">
<a href="https://mothership.sg/author/tanyaong"><span class="author-name ">Tanya Ong</span></a><span class="pipe">|</span>
</span>
<span class="publish-date">
<img class="clock" src="/assets/images/icons/clock.png" />
February 18, 10:53 AM </span>
</p>
</div>
<div class="social-share ">
<a href="#" class="social-fb-share">
<span><img src="/assets/images/icons/svg/fb-icon.svg" /></span>
</a>
